513
00:21:22,625 --> 00:21:25,541
Her legacy? Hold on.

514
00:21:25,625 --> 00:21:27,166
[MAHO]
Meaning...

515
00:21:27,250 --> 00:21:28,958
...I have Kurisu's laptop.

516
00:21:30,333 --> 00:21:32,708
[MAHO] With all her notes
and theories intact.

517
00:21:32,791 --> 00:21:35,625
Her research data
and her private data, too.

518
00:21:35,708 --> 00:21:37,375
Her personal computer.

519
00:21:39,291 --> 00:21:41,458
[MAHO] The burglar who
broke into my hotel,

520
00:21:41,541 --> 00:21:42,791
that must have been
what they wanted.

521
00:21:42,875 --> 00:21:45,208
[OKABE whimpering]
Where is it?

522
00:21:45,291 --> 00:21:47,083
I can't figure out
her password.

