526
00:21:52,000 --> 00:21:54,083
Kurisu's computer
must not be opened!

527
00:21:54,166 --> 00:21:55,666
It's Pandora's Box!

528
00:21:55,750 --> 00:21:57,041
The data inside is a curse

529
00:21:57,125 --> 00:21:59,750
that leads to the annihilation
of the entire globe!

530
00:21:59,833 --> 00:22:00,791
What are you saying?

531
00:22:00,875 --> 00:22:02,208
Don't you hear me?

532
00:22:02,291 --> 00:22:03,833
